{
  "stem": "22734.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I could tell you exactly how my home was furnished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- it was done in-- in oak furniture, which came from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother was very proud of it, and it was made to measure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was sort of brownish, like cherry wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it had no bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a couch, which was a very modern idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the couch was-- it had three mattresses, and they were covered in red.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had a huge desk, which was-- the top of the desk was black linoleum, which was not a very practical thing, but still.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a library behind glass doors, and a glass table, like here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the glass was, again, black.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother got hold of some sort of interior decorator, and it was not really suitable for a young kid, but that's what I had.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had two chairs in red leather, very similar to-- to the one that's here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was like pleated-- the-- the backs were pleated red leather, tomato red.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what I mean by pleated?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's about all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a nuisance, beca-- and there was a big wardrobe there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And if you wanted to make the bed, you had to turn around the mattresses, and the sheets were in a drawer underneath.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I never did it, so-- [LAUGHS] until the war, so then it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was my room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The dining room was very formal, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and it had a round table with four chairs, and-- and two chairs in a corner.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it had a glass-enclosed sort of curio cabinet, where my mother collected all kinds of china, Rosenthal, and [INAUDIBLE], and the figurines.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
